title: Season 2, Episode 4: The Changing Face of American Conservatism
itunes:author: Yuval Levin, Alex Sundstrom, Denise Baron, Chris Gilson
description: Contributor(s): Yuval Levin, Alex Sundstrom, Denise Baron, Chris Gilson | From the party of Ronald Reagan to Donald Trump, the Republican Party is changing, but what caused these changes and where is American conservatism headed? This episode, we dive into these and other questions about the changing face of Republicans, the GOP, and American conservatism.
